===========================================================================
$NetBSD$

For help, type
${PREFIX}/scrc-2.1/bin/scrc -h

Or to compile sample file,
 (rsync -a  ${PREFIX}/scrc-2.1/examples/simple/ /tmp/scrc-simple/ ; \
  cd /tmp/scrc-simple; env PATH=${PREFIX}/scrc-2.1/bin:$PATH make)
===========================================================================
